{"tid":1161351,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Twins出道18年！阿Sa阿嬌遊日孖公仔報喜!!!!!","createTime":"2019-05-19T06:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T11:49:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53453c94b256f016f7a6fe76323db618b43093f6","tid":1161351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190518/photo/bkn-20190518160557550-0518_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190518163342\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190518%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190518160557550-0518_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190518163342&h=74f321b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日係Twins出道18周年嘅大日子，兩位好姊妹蔡卓妍（阿Sa）和鍾欣潼（阿嬌）近日就一齊去日本旅行輕鬆一番，仲喺網上分享旅遊花絮片。片中見到佢哋兩個去咗唔同景點遊覽，食咗好多美食，又齊齊夾公仔，不知幾開心，之後返到酒店又一齊落妝、敷Mask，睇片都睇得出佢哋幾咁享受呢個旅程，阿Sa話：「呢兩個人究竟有乜咁好笑呢？哈哈哈哈哈哈哈!twins今日出道18歲周年呀 !相愛18年，感謝各位鄉親父老一直頂（鼎）力支持，共你即使風沙吹過不再一樣，有一點滄桑都可更為漂亮，風雨同路18年！」 <br />\n<br />\n網友都話佢哋嘅姊妹情非常難得，仲話會繼續支持佢哋更多個18年呀！"},{"pid":"3a9d61586de934ef3d705c8ed6b7073359f8aee3","tid":1161351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190518/mobile/bkn-20190518160557550-0518_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190518%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190518160557550-0518_00862_001.html&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=004eb5c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190518/mobile/bkn-20190518160557550-0518_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e46b1baa622656d2d89148504c5e1a04f7d39286","tid":1161351,"uid":245552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=OOBJEs-Kgxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOOBJEs-Kgxg&d=